cx_freeze windows
- install via pip
- take cx_freeze-quickstart and put it in the folder of the python project to convert
- Do in cmd:
  - cd to the folder project
  - C:\pythonx.y\python.exe cxFreeze-quickstart
  - a setup.py file is created and is proposed to be execute, try it
  - if not working, import package will be requested. It has to be added manually in the setup.py file
  - to exec setup.py: C:\pythonx.y\python.exe setup.py build
  
- with unicurses, 4 files need to be added in the build folder:
  - curses.h
  - panel.h
  - pdcurses.dll
  - pdcurses.lib
